Starts Data Wrangling

avocado_data_trim <- avocado_data %>% 
  clean_names() %>% 
  select(-date, -x, -region, 
         # -x4046, -x4225, -x4770, 
         -total_volume,
         -total_bags) %>% 
  rename(hass_small_4046 = x4046, hass_large_4225 = x4225, hass_xl_4770 = x4770) %>% 
  drop_na()

Observes data for average_price by different variables

Year:

avocado_data_trim %>% 
  group_by(year) %>% 
  ggplot() +
  geom_boxplot(aes(
    x = year,
    y = average_price,
    group = year
  ))

Type:
